    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Something we did not discuss: should a new search be triggered when unmounting the widget? I would say yes: the cleanup must be complete, state and search parameters.\r\n\r\nIf you agree we will have to change the way it's done here, you may need two  methods.",
