  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Before we take \"shortcuts\" because we foresee it will be easier and should be automatic. I would like us to first experiment with it and see how it goes, how users are using it. I am not even sure people will actually ADD to the state if we do enough connectors.\r\n\r\nJust not confident about doing anything \"automatic\" for now. I would rather force us to be explicit for things like state manipulation.",
